TestTagWritesPairsOntoCurrentCall
/ debug.tag attaches Tags to the caller's Call (the surrounding step/goal scope). Subsequent steps reach those tags via Current.Caller.Tags. Tags dict is lazy-allocated.
- debug.tag critical=true, owner=checkout
- assert %!callStack.Current.Caller.Tags.critical% equals "true"
- assert %!callStack.Current.Caller.Tags.owner% equals "checkout"
